    • Field Detail

      • ANCHOR_SEPARATOR

        public static final String ANCHOR_SEPARATOR
        The constant ANCHOR_SEPARATOR holds the character U+00A6 (“¦”) which can be used to separate multiple anchors, if several of them are needed in one project. The anchors must then be listed the hierarchical order they have to be applied, that is the topmost anchor in first place, followed by the second one and so on.
